data.title: Territory Subdivisions
data.text:
Shows the subdivisions of territories, using the Unicode Subdivision Codes with the English names (and sort order). For more information see the LDML spec.

Warning: Do not scrape this chart for production data. Instead, for the meaning of the fields and data consult the LDML specification, and for machine-readable source data, access common/supplemental/subdivisions.xml and common/validity/subdivision.xml.
